InstanceStoreQueryResult Class

Definition

Supports an extensible mechanism to provide data from an instance store. This includes data for instances, instance owners, and instance keys other than those bound to the instance handle being used. For example, a persistence provider mayprovide the owner metadata for all the instance owners in the store by passing an instance of a class derived from InstanceStoreQueryResult to the stem.Runtime.DurableInstancing.InstancePersistenceContext.QueriedInstanceStore*method.
